 asked the Minister for Agriculture, Fisheries and Forestry, upon notice, on 28 June 2010:
Can a list be provided of all members of the Australian Landcare Council (ALC), including:
the member’s name;
the member’s state or territory of residence;
a brief resumé of the member;
the date on which the member was appointed; and
the term of the member’s appointment.
Has the membership of the ALC been publicly announced:
if so:
when, and
did the ALC meet prior to the announcement and what was the purpose of that meeting; and
if not, why not and will the membership be made public, when and how.
